comments: Software License Maintenance. This contract includes one amendment of $33,334.73 bringing the total value of the contract to $309,034.69. This is a multi-year contract that was awarded in February 2013 in the amount of $263,312.73, and amended in April 2013 in the amount of $12,387.23. This contract is a call-up against a Public Works and Government Services Canada procurement tool.
